title: Study Hall: IS IT TIME TO SELL STOCKS, WILL CHINA COLLAPSE, BITCOIN & ETHEREUM
itunes:title: Study Hall: IS IT TIME TO SELL STOCKS, WILL CHINA COLLAPSE, BITCOIN & ETHEREUM
description:
In this Study Hall we talked about Michael Burry recently selling most of his stocks, Ian spoke about the possibility of the fall of China and we talked about the recent rise of crypto, we also discussed if it's a good time to buy Bitcoin and Ethereum. 

Link to Invest Fest Europe: https://investfest.com/euro/
